@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tilkid(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.80) - v0) - (wp.cos(v2 + 0.64) / (v1 + 0.94 - tmp + 0.90)))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v2 + 0.53 + v2 + 0.86)))
    tmp = wp.exp(0.49)
    v2 = (0.65 / v2)
    v1 = wp.exp((v0 + (v1 + 0.49 / v2 + 0.16)))
    data[tid] = v0
